            <div class="title">
                Bombing Of British Ships
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1938-06-23/debates/468fd6c1-71f6-4ee3-93c2-b005cc78cd86/FinanceBill" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
