<p class="">I have made no proposal. I did not make any proposal <span id="1361" class="column-number" data-column-number="1361"></span> in regard to anti-aircraft guns, I said that was a matter for the owners and not for the Government. If the right hon. Gentleman is asking whether the British Government are prepared to issue arms to merchant vessels, the answer is, definitely, no.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
