            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-c92a7479-3f42-43fc-9c18-3bfd0d598a9e">
                Mr. James Griffiths
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
